Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Friedman warns on inflation
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjn7c
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Dec 1976
Nobel economist Milton Friedman warns incoming president on dangers of inflation. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.